            <p>We are The Maelstrom - a World of Warcraft guild on US-Nathrezim server (bundled with Garithos, Chromaggus, Anub'arak, Smolderthorn, and Crushridge). We were formed in 2016 by a rag-tag group of Molten Core raiders. We have been together in at least a limited capacity through Vanilla, The Burning Crusade, Wrath of the Lich King, Cataclysm, Mists of Pandaria, and Warlords of Draenor. We've come together and reclaimed our guild on our original server, to defeat the Burning Legion in World Of Warcraft: Legion (and mostly to have a fun time).
</div>
